Self.Wiki: This map object represents an in-game object of varying sizes, from clutter to cliffs. Supports in-built collision, however not all objects use it.

CollisionName.Wiki: The collision that controls loading of the object.

AnimIDs.Wiki: The animation ID for this object to idle with.

BreakobjID.Wiki: Something to do with breakobj functionality. Possibly decides which part of a shared-map (chalice) .breakobj file to use.
